des:
Please feel free to ask us for a joke like:

Alexa, Ask Car Jokes to tell me a car joke.
Alexa, Tell Car Jokes to give me a joke.
Alexa, Ask Car Jokes for a good one.

In the near future, we will add the ability to call out what is your favorite brand of cars or trucks.
